Its operations cover membership sports and recreation clubs. The company is not involved in the import or export of goods. CRONULLA-SUTHERLAND DISTRICT RUGBY LEAGUE FOOTBALL CLUB LIMITED is headquartered in Woolooware, New South Wales. It is headed by group chief executive officer Dane Sorensen.
